Description: Tobias and the Angel/ The Flight into Egypt: altered from Hercules Seghers; Tobias and the Angel walking on a hillside in the right foreground, a forest behind them and a landscape with a canal and hamlet in the central background; reproduction of the original etching by Hercules Segers before alterations by Rembrandt Photomechanical reproduction
Curator's comments: For an impression of second state and comment see 1848,0911.31.
